      "message": "Not sure I understand your comment: there is no 'componentInstance' any more since it is replaced by 'componentInstanceOpt'.\nIf 'componentInstanceOpt' is empty (equivalent to 'null'), we print the message.\nHowever, since 'componentOpt' could also be empty, we test this first before we trigger a NPE by calling 'component.getName()'.",
