      "file_path": "catalog-be/src/main/java/org/openecomp/sdc/be/components/impl/ArtifactsBusinessLogic.java",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 4711,
      "message": "If 'component' is null, the debug will not be printed since there'll be a NPE when we try to access 'component.getName()'.\n\nThe goal of this CR is to get rid of this NPE (amongst others).",
